  <li>As is to be expected, the Rockies, who play well-above sea level
inÂ Denver, CO, have the highest OPS (though I would argue that the
number is still impressive even after accounting forÂ geography). I
did not adjust for <a href="http://espn.go.com/mlb/stats/parkfactor">park <span style="text-decoration:underline;">factors</span></a>Â in
